    <item>
      <title>१७३ पुरोहित-प्राप्त्युपदेशः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/01_Adiparva/11_chaitrarathaparva/04_vasiShTha-kathA/173_purohita-prAptyupadeshaH/</link>
